item.description:
invalid: <p>
Since <code>selected()</code> is comparing values, you should see if <code>in_array()</code> returns true. And since it can accept that the first value is just true or false, you can just use it as the first argument.
</p>
<pre class="wiki">$value = '1';
selected( in_array( $value, array( '1', '3' ) ) );
</pre>
